24 Future Fund at the direction of the Legislature. Any money in the Tuition
25 Recovery Cash Fund available for investment shall be invested by the
26 state investment officer pursuant to the Nebraska Capital Expansion Act
27 and the Nebraska State Funds Investment Act. Any interest earned by the
28 fund shall accrue to the fund.
